checkers.util
Class QualifierDefaults

java.lang.Object
  checkers.util.QualifierDefaults

public class QualifierDefaults
extends Object

Determines the default qualifiers on a type. Default qualifiers are specified via the DefaultQualifier annotation.

See Also:
DefaultQualifier
